Фермер Лаийон
Крупный долг. Выселен с земли.' WHERE entry=262; /* text: Magistrate Rutherford Burnside All debts settled. Blacksmith Avery Verringtan All debts settled. Clerk Horrace Whitesteed All debts settled. Councilman Gillis All debts settled. Councilman Hooks All debts settled. Farmer Getz All debts settled. Farmer Ray Debt outstanding.  Payment in agricultural goods promised at time of harvest. Farmer Lyion Debt outstanding.  Evicted from the land. */
